WHEREAS, A loving husband to his wife, the late Kathlynne, a 24
devoted father to his four children, Elizabeth, Amy, Laura, and 25
Lynnette, and a doting grandfather to his numerous grandchildren, Ben 26
Espy always used his talents to the benefit of others, and the warmth 27
