as a testament to his personal character. Although the void which his 29
death has created can never be filled, the legacy of care and 30
commitment he established will surely live on; therefore be it 31
RESOLVED, That we, the members of the Senate of the 136th General 32
Assembly of Ohio, in adopting this Resolution, pay tribute to the 33
memory of a truly honorable man, Ben Espy; and be it further 34
RESOLVED, That the Clerk of the Senate transmit a duly 35
authenticated copy of this Resolution to the family of Ben Espy. 36

